    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L straight-six, equipped with individual throttle bodies and double VANOS for exceptional throttle response. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a limited-slip differential, providing classic rear-wheel-drive dynamics. To ensure structural integrity, the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced, and the suspension has been refreshed with Bilstein dampers to maintain factory-plus handling characteristics. It presents in honest condition with a documented service history including recent rod bearing replacement and VANOS solenoid service, making it an ideal candidate for an enthusiast seeking mechanical excellence over garage-queen status.",
