      "description": "This vehicle has been meticulously maintained and serves as a reliable daily driver that still turns heads. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, though you will find the expected minor stone chips on the front bumper and a small superficial scratch near the rear wheel well consistent with regular use. Inside, the cabin is smoke-free and well-preserved; the premium leather seats show only light softening on the driver\u2019s side bolster, and all digital displays and climate controls function perfectly. Mechanically, the car is sound\u2014recent service includes a fresh oil change, brake pad replacement, and a cooling system flush. The tires have plenty of life remaining, providing a smooth and confident ride. Included are two sets of keys and a comprehensive folder of service history. This is a solid, honest example of a well-cared-for car ready for its next owner.",
